# Patrol-drone street encounter dialogue.
# Format: see data/dialogue/school.dlg. One line = one page (click to advance).
# Placeholders {place} {name} {contraband} {signoff} are filled in by
# DroneEncounter.gd via Dialogue.get_pages(..., fmt).
#
# The drone layer changes (it drops in, draws its gun, blinks its camera, flies
# off) are NOT authored here — they live in DroneEncounter.gd, mapped to the
# page index within each section. If you add or remove a line in a section,
# update the matching action indices in DroneEncounter._start().
#
# First encounter plays the full [opening] + [caught]/[clean]. Every encounter
# after that plays the shorter [opening_short] + [caught_short]/[clean_short].

[opening]
[i]The walk home is nice. It's a breath of fresh air after {place}.[/i]
DRONE: HELLO CITIZEN. IDENTIFY YOURSELF.
You: Uh.. Hi. I'm {name}.
DRONE: PROVIDE IDENTIFICATION.
[i]The drone's camera locks onto your hand as you reach into your pocket.[/i]

[opening_short]
[i]Another walk home after {place}. A patrol drone floats down hovers in your way. You know the drill by now.[/i]
DRONE: IDENTIFY YOURSELF. PRESENT IDENTIFICATION.

[caught]
[i]As you reach your hand out to present your ID, you notice that the drone's camera is still pointed at a large lump in your pocket.[/i]
DRONE: WHAT IS THAT IN YOUR POCKET? SHOW ME.
You: It's uhh... it's my... penis.
DRONE: ...
You: ...
DRONE: YOU HAVE THREE SECONDS TO IDENTIFY THE ITEM IN YOUR POCKET.
DRONE: 3... 2...
[i]You rip the {contraband} out of your pocket and present it to the drone.[/i]
DRONE: THIS IS ILLEGAL CONTRABAND.
DRONE: YOU WILL BE FINED AND THIS INCIDENT WILL BE CATALOGUED IN YOUR RECORD.
[i]It drops your id at your feet on the sidewalk.[/i]
DRONE: THANK YOU FOR YOUR COOPERATION, CRIMINAL.
[i]The drone flies away.[/i]
Thoughts: ...Damn.

[caught_short]
[i]The camera fixes on the lump in your pocket...[/i]
Thoughts: Shit.
DRONE: SHOW ME WHAT'S IN YOUR POCKET.
[i]You hand the {contraband} over.[/i]
DRONE: CONTRABAND. YOU WILL BE FINED. THIS INCIDENT WILL REFLECT ON YOUR RECORD.
[i]It drops your id at your feet.[/i]
DRONE: YOUR COOPERATION IS ACKOWLEDGED, CRIMINAL.
[i]The drone flies off.[/i]

[clean]
[i]As you reach for your wallet, you notice the drone's camera scanning you up and down.[/i]
Thoughts: I shouldn't have any contraband on me... I think I'm safe.
[i]You hold out the id to the Patrol Drone.[/i]
DRONE: EVERYTHING APPEARS TO BE IN ORDER. {signoff}
DRONE: THANK YOU FOR YOUR COOPERATION, CITIZEN.
[i]It flies off.[/i]
Thoughts: That was stressful... Good thing I didn't steal anything.

[clean_short]
[i]The drone's camera gives you a quick sweep.[/i]
[i]You hold out your id.[/i]
DRONE: EVERYTHING IS IN ORDER. {signoff}
[i]It flies off.[/i]
